title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8112.11 - Village of Walton
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8112.11 - Village of Walton

State Regulations
(a) Franklin

Road. The eastbound and westbound roadways of Franklin Road between the
northerly Walton village line and Townsend Street, a distance of 0.2+- mile in
the Village of Walton. (b) Townsend

Street. The northbound and southbound roadways of Townsend Street between

Franklin Road and Route 10, a distance of 0.9+- mile in the Village of

Walton. (c) Route 10. The
northbound and southbound roadways of Route 10 between Townsend Street and the
southerly Walton village line, a distance of 1.0+- mile in the Village of

Walton. Notes
